    "The main finding is that the DNN algorithm outperforms traditional machine learning algorithms in predicting health insurance costs.",
    "The conclusion highlights the potential of deep learning algorithms, particularly DNN, in revolutionizing cost prediction in the healthcare insurance sector, enabling insurance companies to develop more precise and timely insurance programs tailored to individual characteristics, leading to improved customer satisfaction and operational efficiency.",
